{"attribute_table": [{"attribute_type": "Variant", "attribute_value": "Vacuum-lock suction mechanism", "rank": 1}, {"attribute_type": "Variant", "attribute_value": "24 N52 magnet dual-ring system", "rank": 2}, {"attribute_type": "Variant", "attribute_value": "MagSafe-compatible magnetic mount", "rank": 3}, {"attribute_type": "Variant", "attribute_value": "360° swivel with 180° tilt adjustment", "rank": 5}, {"attribute_type": "Variant", "attribute_value": "Foldable and retractable arm", "rank": 6}, {"attribute_type": "Use Case", "attribute_value": "hands-free driving navigation", "rank": 1}, {"attribute_type": "Use Case", "attribute_value": "dashboard or windshield phone mounting", "rank": 2}, {"attribute_type": "Audience", "attribute_value": "drivers", "rank": 1}, {"attribute_type": "Audience", "attribute_value": "rideshare drivers", "rank": 2}], "bullet_points": "Vacuum Lock + Gel Base — For Smooth, Flat Surfaces: Features a rotary vacuum-lock and 4-layer washable gel base that forms a rock-solid hold on flat, non-textured surfaces such as glass, glossy dashboards, or hard leather. Avoid use on curved, soft, or textured materials. To install, firmly press the gel base and rotate the vacuum lock clockwise until tight
Washable Gel Base — Restores Grip After Rinsing: The reusable nano-gel base maintains strong adhesion when clean. If suction weakens due to dust or dirt, simply rinse the gel with water and let it air dry—this restores up to 99% of its original stickiness, and built to withstand -40°F to 194°F
360° Customizable Viewing Angle: Achieve full viewing flexibility with triple-axis adjustment—360° swivel, 180° tilt, and foldable arm positioning. Effortlessly switch between portrait and landscape modes. Built-in zinc alloy hinges rated for 7,000+ adjustments
